      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Jul 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/0.45.1-relnotes/</guid>
      <description>&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;This is a bug-fix release with a couple of important fixes (and one enhancement).&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;enhancements&#34;&gt;Enhancements&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Add Page.FirstSection &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/commit/016dd4a69a765061bb3da8490d3cac6ec47a91eb&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;016dd4a6&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/bep&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;@bep&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;fixes&#34;&gt;Fixes&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Fix .Site.GetPage regression &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/commit/04d4c08dbcac08ff7feeb88863e91799fed0937b&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;04d4c08d&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/bep&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;@bep&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4989&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;#4989&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Fix &amp;ldquo;borrow content from another language&amp;rdquo; issue &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/commit/c6b599a06d66b8e3c92343d25bb8043eb4f291f1&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;c6b599a0&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/bep&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;@bep&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4986&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;#4986&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
